lead_paragraph: Deion Branch will not make his Seahawks debut today against the Arizona Cardinals. Seattle would have had to release a player from its 53-man roster by yesterday afternoon to add Branch, who was acquired Monday from New England. A team spokesman confirmed that the Seahawks did not release a player.
